WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.520
Welcome, everybody, to the Data Science Hangout. I know that most of you have all been here

00:00:08.520 --> 00:00:15.000
before, so welcome back. But for anyone who's just joining, this is an open space for current

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:21.000
and aspiring data science leaders, everybody across the data science community, to connect

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:25.520
and chat about some of the more human-centric questions around data science leadership.

00:00:26.080 --> 00:00:31.520
And so we really want to create this space where everybody can participate and we can hear from

00:00:31.520 --> 00:00:38.000
everyone. So there's a few different ways that you can jump in and ask questions. You could just

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:44.240
unmute yourself and ask questions live. You could put questions in the chat. And we also have a

00:00:44.240 --> 00:00:49.439
