I think. When I started at Promforma, which was like four years ago, we had three data scientists,

00:03:22.880 --> 00:03:27.679
and it was sort of just this side project that the organization was vaguely considering. Someone

00:03:27.679 --> 00:03:32.880
said, you should put some money into data science, and there were some analysts already there who

00:03:32.880 --> 00:03:38.960
were interested, and so they formed this very small data science team. I think maybe the second

